     And I'm ready to
     spoon-feed you a delicious
     mouthful of pain.

13:43.523 --> 13:45.423
         I'll see ya ladle.

13:46.660 --> 13:48.626
 Looking for something?

13:48.628 --> 13:50.495
             Cut! Cut. Cut.

13:50.497 --> 13:52.096
         You're not selling it,
         Dave Kim.

13:52.098 --> 13:54.599
           Think about how dumb
           your haircut is.

13:54.601 --> 13:55.834
                 Use your pain.

13:55.836 --> 13:58.303
       Gah!
       Steady up the boom, Taz.

